---
title: Caramelised Onion-Glazed Chicken with Garlic-Herb Roasted Veggies & Pear Salad
description: Hold onto your forks, because we're predicting a flurry of excitement when this delectable chicken hits the table! With a glaze of caramelised onion and parsley, it has a mountain of flavour, and we've added garlic-herb roasted veggies and a refreshing pear salad to seal the deal.
